            <title>[SPARK-31468] Null types should be implicitly casted to Decimal types</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-31468</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A query below fails in master/branch-3.0 and passed in v2.4.5;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
scala&amp;gt; Seq(BigDecimal(10)).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;v1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).selectExpr(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;v1 = NULL&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).explain(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;)
org.apache.spark.sql.AnalysisException: cannot resolve &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;(`v1` = NULL)&apos;&lt;/span&gt; due to data type mismatch: differing types in &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;(`v1` = NULL)&apos;&lt;/span&gt; (decimal(38,18) and &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;).; line 1 pos 0;
&apos;Project [(v1#5 = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) AS (v1 = NULL)#7]
+- Project [value#2 AS v1#5]
   +- LocalRelation [value#2]
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
